# Test binary, built with `go test -c`
*.test

# Output of the go coverage tool
*.out
coverage.html

# Go workspace file
#
# praxis is a multi-module monorepo (core + praxis/mcp, plus praxis/skills
# from v0.9.0). The go.work file at the repo root is committed intentionally
# so local dev and CI exercise every workspace module in a single command
# (see Makefile MODULE_PATHS). go.work is NOT included in Go module zips,
# so external consumers of either module never see it.
#
# go.work is intentionally NOT ignored.
# go.work.sum is intentionally NOT ignored (transitive-dep reproducibility).

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
